:200971,"uid":2547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T03:28:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以前既紅藥水好好用<br />\n倒少少係面過一陣就止血<br />\n依家個啲好流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n紅汞是含螢光素母體的有機汞二鈉鹽，其結晶有綠色金屬光澤，可用作殺菌劑，其2%溶液稱為紅藥水。由於含汞且作用較差，現已很少使用<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有水銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></blockquote><br />\n藍藥水- 由於其顏色的濃烈及脫色的難度，注重外表的人一般也不會將它應用在易見的皮膚上。擁有潛在的<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">致癌性</span></span>，故此現今不少醫院、診所等醫療機構已不選用藍藥水"},{"pid":"c35811715e02f660b45a66872d9fb679fd2115cb","tid":200971,"uid":48738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T04:44:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>以前既紅藥水好好用<br />\n倒少少係面過一陣就止血<br />\n依家個啲好流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n紅汞是含螢光素母體的有機汞二鈉鹽，其結晶有綠色金屬光澤，可用作殺菌劑，其2%溶液稱為紅藥水。由於含汞且作用較差，現已很少使用<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有水銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></blockquote><br />\n藍藥水- 由於其顏色的濃烈及脫色的難度，注重外表的人一般也不會將它應用在易見的皮膚上。擁有潛在的<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">致癌性</span></span>，故此現今不少醫院、診所等醫療機構已不選用藍藥水</blockquote><br />\n所以停產左"},{"pid":"c0e44d9ce74c7f7227c9432884a47ba9988959b8","tid":200971,"uid":44559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T04:48:59.000Z","msg":"3隻有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"335b9dac380f90a88354ba2ae030a26ee3ed273a","tid":200971,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:16:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>以前既紅藥水好好用<br />\n倒少少係面過一陣就止血<br />\n依家個啲好流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n紅汞是含螢光素母體的有機汞二鈉鹽，其結晶有綠色金屬光澤，可用作殺菌劑，其2%溶液稱為紅藥水。由於含汞且作用較差，現已很少使用<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有水銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></blockquote><br />\n藍藥水- 由於其顏色的濃烈及脫色的難度，注重外表的人一般也不會將它應用在易見的皮膚上。擁有潛在的<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">致癌性</span></span>，故此現今不少醫院、診所等醫療機構已不選用藍藥水</blockquote><br />\n所以停產左</blockquote><br />\n我都係搵到類似嘅資料<br />\n但貌似就搵唔到停產或者禁用新聞<br />\n<br />\nbtw thx <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2360da2994635ac4081b5ace7e612b84896c48c4","tid":200971,"uid":40867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:16:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>3隻有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都唔知<br />\n好似就係受傷即時用消毒同傷口護理嘅分別"},{"pid":"008ece6ca6eba13b96993f4861317bb1ca08af65","tid":200971,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:19:15.000Z","msg":"紅藥水搽完好似流血咁會嚇親人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dde2254ff53cba2827447bd0404e58b8ef698e01","tid":200971,"uid":7378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T06:08:43.000Z","msg":"而家醫院用既洗傷口藥水有Unisept(Hibitane), Tisept(Salvon)"}]}